data.description: Nestled in the sought-after Mount Helix neighborhood, this inviting home sits on a spacious private lot. The residence features a welcoming open layout, perfect for both day-to-day living and entertaining guests. Step outside to your very own outdoor oasis with mature fruit trees and tropical landscaping surrounding a large inground heated, pool and spa await, providing a serene retreat with the added ambiance of underwater lighting. Embrace energy efficiency with owned solar panels and dual-zone air conditioning, ensuring a comfortable environment year-round. Inside, recent upgrades enhance the home's appeal, including new hardwood flooring in all bedrooms, refinished stairs, and modern window treatments. Security and convenience are paramount with a gated property, a new main gate, and the added perk of an included E-car charger. Enjoy the flexibility of additional space, making this property ideal for those considering an Additional Dwelling Unit (ADU).The primary bedroom serves as a relaxing retreat, complete with a large sitting area, deep soaking tub and a spacious walk-in closet. This home seamlessly blends modern amenities with practical features, offering a comfortable and convenient lifestyle.
